<note n="0211005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0211005">Ghatāsana（食酪者＝聖火）。</note>
<note n="0212001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0212001">讀為 buddho' Si（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0213001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0213001">Sugandha（芳香）。</note>
