<note n="0214002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0214002">讀為 sattāsuṁ（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0215003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0215003">訂正為 thavitvā。</note>
<note n="0215004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0215004">Paṭhavidundubī（地鼓）。</note>
