<note n="0215011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0215011">Rājāvilokana（王省察）。</note>
<note n="0215012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0215012">Hirisāra（恥髓）。</note>
<note n="0217001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0217001">Dhaññavatī（穀市）。</note>
<note n="0217002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0217002">Varadassana（勝見）。</note>
<note n="0218001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0218001">Puṇḍarīka 為白蓮華，但在此可視為與尸棄佛之路樹為同一種樹。</note>
