<note n="0219001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0219001">Puḷinapupphiya（砂花）。</note>
<note n="0220001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0220001">gaṇṭhi 樹名。</note>
<note n="0221001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0221001">Jaluttama（最勝水）。</note>
<note n="0222001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0222001">Thomaka = thavika 即指 Sammukhathāvika 而言。</note>
